          </div>
          <p class="hero-trust">Developed for licensed professionals supporting clients navigating anxiety, depression, OCD, ADHD, insomnia, addiction, chronic pain, and eating disorders.</p>
        </article>
        <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="hero-showcase">
            <div class="hero-showcase-card">
              <h3>Inside the Mega Bundle</h3>
              <ul class="hero-showcase-list">
                <li>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                  </svg>
                  100+ therapist-crafted CBT tools
                </li>
                <li>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2" />
                    <path d="M7 8h10M7 12h6" />
                  </svg>
                  Worksheets, cards, journals &amp; trackers
                </li>
                <li>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
